Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:19.09,piantou,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽水和苹果糖「备」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是祭典的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我想住哪里就住哪里的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发明？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要抓住上面的竹棒搬着走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能走到任何地方的小房子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是要到接近镇子的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是去找工作的话真是很方便哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们马上来试验一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的游泳池——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要生日礼物了  给我买塑料游泳池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不久前才给你买的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破了一个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漏气了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我们家花钱就是花在这上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很可怜但是不能再买给你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是第四个了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:47.87,charu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(木鱼占卜)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  祭典店铺的位置由掉出珠子的颜色决定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了就不能有怨言了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那么从第一个人开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小练也要选位吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  掉出金色的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我选在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  被抢占了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.94,charu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(中央市民游泳池)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一张小孩的票
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么声音  老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是一年一度的夏祭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些就是通知大家今天是祭典的烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚好像还将举行盂兰盆会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盂兰盆会？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个的话我也知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是舞会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…水…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有人倒在那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…水…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想喝水吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？还是…有点…头晕晕的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  这是爷爷的酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:06:01.78,charu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(祈福)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:09.11,charu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(灵验 祈福 木鱼占卜)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把木鱼放上去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了  感觉静不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:18.86,charu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(夏日祭典)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备长炭～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么工作做完以后要过来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在台阶上面的鸟居那里等你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:35.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（鸟居：日本神社门口的牌坊一类的建筑物）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  一会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日祭典  她也会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用午餐的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要玩  我也要玩  我也要玩～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  来试试吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是一开始就用力哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是在木锤接触鼓面的瞬间用力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要找的东西在南边的方位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多店铺哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典真是太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧丸子～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头晕晕的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但祭典真是太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备长炭好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后把这些垃圾扔掉  今天的工作就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你做到这么晚  真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是一个普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也会是平常的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好也罢坏也罢  全都会很平常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备长炭就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备长炭——
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来的好晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典都快完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  我买好了苹果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹林也在等你哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又感觉静不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中感觉怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你一件好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰你们一下可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了太多的奖品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝不完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们帮我们帮！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给您买了这个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是一种叫做「汽水」的饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是「汽水」?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想要尝一尝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背上突然感觉好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个青色火球钻进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我弄出去啦——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！
