Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢走  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用这个买一身新衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多加小心  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  学到这里大家还有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  这里是镇公所孩童传达问事处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:43.36,charu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩童接待处
